data.title: Ozzy Osbourne Biography, Wikipedia, Age, Children, Wife, Siblings, Parents, Net Worth
data.meta_description: Popular English singer, songwriter, and actor Ozzy Osbourne first rose to prominence as Black Sabbath's lead vocalist.
data.text:
Ozzy Osbourne Biography

The son of Jack and Lillian Osbourne, Ozzy Osbourne was born on December 3, 1948, in Marston Green, England.

Ozzy Osbourne Siblings

Paul Osbourne, Jean Osbourne, Iris Osbourne, Gillian Osbourne, and Tony Osbourne are Ozzy Osbourne’s five siblings.

Parents

John Thomas “Jack” Osbourne and Lillian Osbourne are the parents of Ozzy Osbourne.

Ozzy Osbourne Wife

At the moment, Ozzy Osbourne is married to Sharon Osbourne. Since 1982, they have been married.

Ozzy Osbourne Children

Kelly Osbourne, Aimee Osbourne, Jack Osbourne, Jessica Starshine Osbourne, Elliot Kingsley, and Louis Osbourne are Ozzy Osbourne’s six children.

Ozzy Osbourne Net Worth

The estimated net worth of Ozzy Osbourne is $220 million. He is one of the wealthiest actors, musicians, and singers in the world.
